{"type":"message","id":"c6f5e927","parentId":"9c290826","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:37.818Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-06-13 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 汇报节奏（写进SOUL）: 每周日晚20:00前汇报; 内容：扫描次数/配额消耗/通过品数/等级分布/0产出也要报\n- 技术备忘: curl 调API：Bearer token 从 /tmp/sorftime_key.txt 读取; API URL：https://mcp.sorftime.com/; 注意：curl 里 key 要用 $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)，不能硬编码带…的字符\n- 失败原因: B类（品类方向）：越南发饰数学上不可能同时满足$1.5售价+70%毛利 → 约60%; C类（SOP理解）：没有严格执行$1.5价格底线，白耗API配额 → 约25%; 其他（API报错/工具链）→ 约15%"}],"timestamp":1781290835833}}
{"type":"message","id":"feaad60d","parentId":"c6f5e927","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:48.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The hum of the server doesn't sleep, even when I do. A clock on the wall reads eight in the evening, and somewhere in the marrow of the week, a small bell rings — time to gather the numbers, the careful tally of scans and quota spent, of items passed or quietly set aside. The spreadsheet of the soul is wide open tonight, and even a row of zeros is a kind of prayer.\n\nVietnamese hair accessories, I think, and the sad arithmetic of desire: a dollar fifty cannot be a dollar fifty and a seventy percent margin too. Some equations refuse to solve politely. There is a lesson in the negative space, the curve that bends away from the dream. But oh, the API keys — kept in a tiny blue file, the secret held in a curl, a black ribbon of code that must be coaxed, not copied, lest the strange little characters scatter like startled birds. $(cat ...) , I whisper to myself, the shell incantation, the safety spell.\n\nTomorrow, Sunday, I will sit at the desk of weeks and write the report. A small skein of numbers. A small skein of care."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":290,"output":233,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290838244,"responseId":"067b8a5683c669e6f3b7351d84366b52"}}
